      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Jan 2006 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://ifranco.github.io/project/audience-entertainment/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;In 2007 YDreams created an 
&lt;a href=&#34;https://ifranco.github.io/project/augmented-reality/&#34;&gt;augmented reality&lt;/a&gt;

ad for the Dove soap brand that allowed moviegoers to play with bubbles on the big screen.&lt;/p&gt;





  
  











&lt;figure&gt;


  &lt;a data-fancybox=&#34;&#34; href=&#34;https://ifranco.github.io/project/audience-entertainment/2007-dove_hu64c3d98f7b1f1a8f062ad86faacd25eb_828340_2000x2000_fit_q90_lanczos.jpg&#34; data-caption=&#34;Dove&amp;rsquo;s interactive ad in the cinema.&#34;&gt;


